ISIS-II PL/M-86 V1.0 COMPILATION OF MODULE MONITOR
OBJECT MODULE PLACED IN :F1:SBCMON.OBJ
COMPILER INVOKED BY:  :F2:PLM86 :F1:SBCMON.PLM LARGE OPTIMIZE(2) PRINT(:F3:SBCMON.LST) &
